+ 		/* RFC7540#10.3: intermediaries forwarding to HTTP/1 must take care of
+-		 * rejecting NUL, CR and LF characters.
++		 * rejecting NUL, CR and LF characters. For :path we reject all CTL
++		 * chars, spaces, and '#'.
+ 		 */
